title: I WILL MAKE IT
itunes:title: I WILL MAKE IT
itunes:subtitle: Motiversity
description:
YOU WILL MAKE IT! If you quit now then they'll be right about you. Your life is a result of the choices you make, it will take time but if you DON'T GIVE UP you will make it through, stronger than ever before.


New Motivational Speeches Compilation featuring some of the best motivational speeches by Coach Pain (https://bit.ly/CoachPainMotiversity), Walter Bond (https://bit.ly/WalterBondMotiversity), and Marcus Taylor (https://bit.ly/MarcusTaylorMotiversity).



Music by Really Slow Motion (https://bit.ly/RSMMusic), Succession Studios (https://bit.ly/SecessionStudiosYouTube), and Audiojungle (https://audiojungle.net/).


Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
